eruniface_104qir1665702673146.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qir1665702673146.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qir1665702673146.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qir1665702673146\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specifies the port number on which the Apache Tomcat web server listens for HTTP\n      requests.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"qir1665702673146__topic_d145109e1_d145110e1_d145111e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qir1665702673146__p_d145112e1_d145113e1_d145114e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">Tomcat_Port</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">PortNumber</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"qir1665702673146__section_w3144ab1b5b3_w3145ab1b5_w3146ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qir1665702673146__p_d145115e1_d145116e1_d145117e1\">For example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">tomcat_port=8086</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"qir1665702673146__section_w3147ab1b5b5_w3148ab1b5_w3149ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"qir1665702673146__table_d17663e1_d17664e1_d17665e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">First available port starting with 8080</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">File section: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"efz1665702672861.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/efz1665702672861.html\" title=\"The [install] section of the initialization file contains information about the current installation.\">[install]</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qir1665702673146__section_v3w_pfp_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d933132e114\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The default Uniface installation installs an Apache Tomcat Web Server as part of the\n            Uniface test environment.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cff1665702741216.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Apache Tomcat</a><p>Apache Tomcat is an open-source Java EE (Enterprise Edition)-compliant web server which is included in the Uniface installation.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531282\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531282\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Tomcat_Port Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 22, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specifies the port number on which the Apache Tomcat web server listens for HTTP requests. Tomcat_Port = PortNumber For example: tomcat_port=8086 Default value: First available port starting with 8080 File section: [install] Description The default Uniface installation installs an Apache Tomcat Web Server as part of the Uniface test environment. Related Links Apache Tomcat Apache Tomcat is an open-source Java EE (Enterprise Edition)-compliant web server which is included in the Uniface installation. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}